## Troubleshooting & Recovery

### Common Issues & Solutions

| Issue | Cause | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| High memory usage | Large signal batches | Implement pagination, batch processing |
| Slow detection | Inefficient NLP | Use GPU, cache models, optimize algorithms |
| Database timeouts | Connection pool exhausted | Increase pool size, optimize queries |
| API rate limiting | Too many requests | Implement caching, queue requests |
| Forecast inaccuracy | Insufficient historical data | Use simple forecast, collect more data |

### Recovery Procedures

```bash
# If database is corrupted
docker-compose down
docker volume rm foresight_postgres_data
docker-compose up -d
python manage.py migrate

# If Elasticsearch is out of sync
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:9200/foresight_signals
python manage.py reindex_signals

# If services are stuck
docker-compose restart
```

